Class SolvedExamController

  • java.lang.Object
    • Controllers.SolvedExamController

  • public class SolvedExamController
extends java.lang.Object
    This controller is responsible for all information that has to do with solved exams it has functionality such as adding/editing solved exams also getting solved exams for informational purpeses.
